cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks, specifically image classification, and proposes a new data augmentation method using neural style transfer. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also evaluates the effectiveness of this method using deep learning algorithms, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves image processing techniques, which could be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.GR (Graphics).
